query:
INSERT INTO email_links (id, macro_id, fusionauth_user_id, email_address, provider, is_sync_active)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT (fusionauth_user_id, email_address, provider) 
        DO UPDATE SET 
            is_sync_active = EXCLUDED.is_sync_active,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING id
